#defaults.yml
#Here we can put general information like the Username and Password we will us on each host, or the platform that the device use.

---
platform: cisco_ios               # This field is critical, it's used by the "netmiko_plugin" to map all supported devices "device_type". This specifies the device structure (Cisco XR, Cisco XE, JunOS..) needed and the type of connection used (SSH, Telnet, Serial)
username: ciscouser               #username to login into devices
